import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
CaseData=pd.read_csv("CasesAddTaiwan.csv")
Date=CaseData["Date"]
CaseAddNum=CaseData["Taiwan"]
plt.xticks(rotation =60)
ticker_spacing =10

cases = plt.gca() 
cases.plot(Date,CaseAddNum)
cases.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MultipleLocator(ticker_spacing))
plt.rcParams["font.sans-serif"] = ["Arial Unicode MS"] 

plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
from IPython.core.pylabtools import figsize
import pylab as pl
plt.xticks(rotation =60)
Data=pd.read_csv("AirlineAndCase.csv")
Date=Data["日期"]
DailyEntry=Data["Entry"]
DailyExit=Data["Exit"]
CaseAddNum=Data["cases"]

unit1 = plt.gca() 
unit1.plot(Date,DailyEntry,color="dodgerblue",label="總入境人數")
unit1.plot(Date,DailyExit,color="orange",label="總出境人數")

unit1.set_title("出入境人數與境外確診數之比較")
unit1.set_ylabel("出入境人數")
unit1.set_xlabel("日期")
plt.rcParams["font.sans-serif"] = ["Arial Unicode MS"] 

ticker_spacing =1
unit1.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MultipleLocator(ticker_spacing))
plt.figure(figsize(100,3))

plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
from IPython.core.pylabtools import figsize
plt.xticks(rotation =60)
Data=pd.read_csv("AirlineAndCase.csv")
Date=Data["日期"]
DailyEntry=Data["Entry"]
DailyExit=Data["Exit"]
CaseAddNum=Data["cases"]


Airline = plt.gca() 
Airline.plot(Date,DailyEntry,color="darkorange",label="總入境人數")
Airline.plot(Date,DailyExit,color="slateblue",label="總出境人數")

Airline.set_title("每日總出入境人數", fontsize=40)
Airline.set_ylabel("出入境人數", fontsize=30)
Airline.set_xlabel("日期", fontsize=30)
plt.rcParams["font.sans-serif"] = ["Arial Unicode MS"] 
plt.xticks(fontsize=20)
plt.yticks(fontsize=20)
plt.legend(labels=["總入境人數","總出境人數"], fontsize=30)

ticker_spacing =5
Airline.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MultipleLocator(ticker_spacing))
plt.figure(figsize(40,10))

plt.show()
